| ECS Fargate | Multi-AZ, multi-region | N/A | {status:colour=Green|title=High} | {status:colour=Green|title=Yes} | AP |
| Cognito | Long-lived tokens + backup | {status:colour=Green|title=Strong} | {status:colour=Green|title=High} | {status:colour=Yellow|title=Partial} | CP + graceful degradation |
| Bedrock | Cross-region fallback | N/A | {status:colour=Green|title=High} | {status:colour=Green|title=Yes} | AP |
| Lambda + API GW | Multi-region, DLQ | N/A | {status:colour=Green|title=High} | {status:colour=Green|title=Yes} | AP |
| CloudFront | Global CDN + WAF | {status:colour=Yellow|title=Eventual} | {status:colour=Green|title=High} | {status:colour=Green|title=Yes} | AP |

